      <name>Carl F. Mela, Jason M. T. Roos, Tulio Sousa</name>
    </author>
    <content>&lt;b&gt;Marketing Science&lt;/b&gt; &lt;br&gt;By pooling information across many advertisers, direct buy ad networks can alleviate advertiser uncertainty about where to place ads, increasing publisher revenue and advertiser welfare.</content>
